item.title: CVE-2023-0443|2024-08-02T05:10:56.330Z -- unknown -- anywhere%20elementor
item.description: The AnyWhere Elementor WordPress plugin before 1.2.8 discloses a Freemius Secret Key which could be used by an attacker to purchase the pro subscription using test credit card numbers without actually paying the amount. Such key has been revoked.
